title: Slaughterhouse - House Rules mixtape
description:
After hinting for a few weeks, Slaughterhouse finally releases their new anticipated mixtape "House Rules." The 10 track mixtape is the groups second mixtape collectively and the follow up to the successful "On The House" project. Follow on twitter @JoeBudden @RoyceDa59 @CrookedIntriago @JoellOrtiz


1.House Rules (Intro) (Prod by 8 Bars) 
2.SayDatThen (Prod by Nottz) 
3.Illmind Interlude (Prod by Illmind) 
4.Trade It All (Prod by Dark Knight, 8 Bars) 
5.Keep It 100 (Prod by AraabMuzik) 
6.Offshore (Prod by DJ Pain 1) 
7.Struggle (Prod by Tabu) 
8.Life In The City (Prod by Heatmakerz) 
9.I Aint Bullshittin (Prod by AraabMuzik) 
10.I Dont Know (Prod by Harry Fraud)
